{"tid":384143,"cid":5,"subCid":0,"title":"沿岸現「簡體字」垃圾　黃錦星稱整體垃圾本地為本　指港人責任不可放輕","createTime":"2017-09-02T05:39:05.000Z","updateTime":"2017-09-02T06:04:50.000Z","uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":12,"uniUserReply":0,"replies":[{"pid":"08f7e45108f2b3d74fe3cbc4b6386adddf7c9db4","tid":384143,"uid":53379,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:39:05.000Z","msg":"<span style=\"font-size: xx-large;\"><strong>沿岸現「簡體字」垃圾　黃錦星稱整體垃圾本地為本　指港人責任不可放輕</strong></span><br />\n<br />\n<img src=\"https://fs.mingpao.com/ins/20170902/s00001/8477fdb5eda663d1077c389db0e5747b.jpg\" data-thumbnail-src=\"https://i.lih.kg/thumbnail?u=https%3A%2F%2Ffs.mingpao.com%2Fins%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F8477fdb5eda663d1077c389db0e5747b.jpg&h=d7a1aa86&s={SIZE}\" /><br />\n<br />\n環境局長黃錦星今早出席商台節目，談及香港海岸垃圾，強調大家都有責任保護環境，「（海岸垃圾）有些是區域影響，有些是本地影響。都想強調，我們自己的沿岸垃圾，整體來說，大部分是我們本地自己產生」。<br />\n<br />\n至於本港沿岸地區不時出現印上「簡體字」的垃圾，黃錦星表示，個別地區及個別風向下，「區域影響可以是大」，但整體來說香港不同海岸的垃圾，「根據過去調查，本地為本」，強調「本地人自己責任不可放輕」。<br />\n<br />\n黃錦星又提到，內地收緊進口廢料政策，對本港回收業有危有機，因為內地提高進口廢物質素，可以令回收業提高水平。他又說，因為香港生活習慣以及消費文化，減廢仍是大挑戰，要各方落實藍圖才有機會改善。<br />\n<br />\n<a href=\"https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504319263089\" data-sr-url=\"https://r.lihkg.com/link?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504319263089&d=3E2S4kqCu%2B4ZpRspNF8hZpWUQYxlHU4vp7GM3pu%2FB4U%3D&h=0b5f756e\" data-ef-url=\"https://embed.lih.kg/frame?u=https%3A%2F%2Fm.mingpao.com%2Fins%2Finstantnews%2Fweb_tc%2Farticle%2F20170902%2Fs00001%2F1504319263089&h=9e88a6d9\" target=\"_blank\">https://m.mingpao.com/ins/instantnews/web_tc/article/20170902/s00001/1504319263089</a><br />\n<br />\n又賴落香港人到<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"f794ed0264624da0b8257a97ee618cfc0bfa28d8","tid":384143,"uid":7688,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T05:58:13.000Z","msg":"正仆街黎<br />\n一開口就屈本地人<br />\n比主持質簡體字都可以繼續屈<br />\n屌大陸狗大撚晒咩<img src=\"/assets/faces/normal/dead.gif\" class=\"hkgmoji\" />"},{"pid":"03ef026da2ed15061e5e836d5db2912ea2e3e0ab","tid":384143,"uid":49588,"like":0,"dislike":0,"score":0,"citedBy":0,"replyTime":"2017-09-02T06:04:50.000Z","msg":"賣港可以賣到幾盡！"}]}